Definitely 5 stars for the Doctor. As parents we also felt comfortable and happy seeing our son getting rid of fear with dental issues.Thank you so much Dr. Ajay Mohan for the wonderful service.

review: I had my wisdom tooth removed along with a root canal for adjacent tooth with Impressions. The treatment and service is highly professional and satisfactory.
